        <h2>1. Service Description</h2>
        <p>CC3PO provides AI-powered business solutions including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Website audits, security scans, and performance analysis</li>
          <li>AI chatbots and automated customer support</li>
          <li>AI voice agents and phone answering systems</li>
          <li>HIPAA compliance tools and scanners</li>
          <li>Content generation and marketing automation</li>
          <li>IT consulting and technical support</li>
          <li>Monthly subscription services and managed solutions</li>
